antimage_mana_break.desc: Burns an opponent's mana on each attack.  Mana Break deals 50% of the mana burned as damage to the target. Mana Break has 50% effect if caused by illusions.

antimage_blink.desc: Short distance teleportation that allows Anti-Mage to move in and out of combat.

antimage_spell_shield.desc: Increases Anti-Mage's resistance to magic damage.

antimage_counterspell.desc: Passively grants you magic resistance. Can be activated to create an anti-magic shell around you that sends any targeted spells back towards enemies instead of affecting you.

antimage_mana_void.desc: For each point of mana missing by the target unit, damage is dealt to it and surrounding enemies.  The main target is also mini-stunned.

antimage_mana_overload.desc: Blinks an illusion at the target enemy or location and attack them for 7 seconds. Counterspell is replicated on the Blink Fragment illusion.

axe_berserkers_call.desc: Axe taunts nearby enemy units, forcing them to attack him, while he gains bonus armor during the duration.

axe_battle_hunger.desc: Enrages an enemy unit, causing it to be slowed and take damage over time until it kills another unit or the duration ends. Axe gains movement speed for each unit affected with Battle Hunger, half speed from creeps.

axe_counter_helix.desc: When attacked, Axe has a chance to perform a helix counter attack, dealing pure damage to all nearby enemies.

axe_culling_blade.desc: Axe spots a weakness and strikes, instantly killing an enemy unit with low health, or dealing moderate damage otherwise. When an enemy hero is killed with Culling Blade, its cooldown is reset, and Axe and nearby allied units gain bonus movement speed.

bane_enfeeble.desc: Lowers the enemy's total attack damage, cast speed, and regeneration.

bane_brain_sap.desc: Feasts on the vital energies of an enemy unit, healing Bane and dealing damage.

bane_fiends_grip.desc: CHANNELED - Grips an enemy unit, disabling it and causing heavy damage over time, while stealing mana every 0.5 seconds based on the unit's maximum mana.

bane_nightmare.desc: Puts the target enemy or friendly Hero to sleep. Sleeping units are awakened when damaged. If the target was directly attacked, the Nightmare passes to the attacking unit. Bane can attack nightmared targets freely.

bloodseeker_bloodrage.desc: Drives Bloodseeker into a bloodthirsty rage which causes him to attack faster and deal more spell damage at the cost of a percentage of his health per second. Provides half attack speed to allied heroes.

bloodseeker_blood_bath.desc: Bloodseeker baptizes an area in sacred blood. After 2.9 seconds the ritual completes, causing any enemies caught in the area to take damage and become silenced.

bloodseeker_thirst.desc: Bloodseeker is invigorated by the wounds of his enemies, restoring some life when he kills an enemy unit. Also gains bonus movement speed when an enemy hero's health falls below 75%, with the bonuses increasing as their health falls further. If an enemy hero's health falls below 25%, he will also gain vision and True Sight of that hero. Bonuses stack per hero. Unlocks max movement speed for Bloodseeker.

bloodseeker_rupture.desc: Causes an enemy unit's skin to rupture, dealing initial damage based on its current health. If the unit moves, it takes damage based on the distance moved.  The damage is dealt through spell immunity.

drow_ranger_frost_arrows.desc: Adds a freezing effect to Drow's attacks, slowing enemy movement and dealing bonus damage.  Slow lasts 1.5 seconds.

drow_ranger_multishot.desc: Channeling. Drow releases a flurry of arrows in continuous salvos, hitting enemies for extra damage and applying longer duration Frost Arrows. Lasts up to 1.75 seconds.

drow_ranger_silence.desc: Stops all enemy units in a target area from casting spells.

drow_ranger_wave_of_silence.desc: Releases a wave that silences and knocks back enemy units. Knockback distance is relative to how close they are to Drow.

drow_ranger_trueshot.desc: Adds bonus damage to the physical attack of allied, ranged Hero units based on a percentage of Drow's agility.  Affects creeps for 30 seconds when cast.

drow_ranger_marksmanship.desc: Drow's experiences in battle grant her a chance to launch arrows with incredible accuracy and effectiveness. Pierces through the enemy's defenses, ignoring their base armor. Grants Drow and nearby ranged heroes with bonus agility based on Drow's current agility. This ability is disabled if there is an enemy hero within 400 range.

earthshaker_fissure.desc: Slams the ground with a mighty totem, creating an impassable ridge of stone while stunning and damaging enemy units along its line.

earthshaker_enchant_totem.desc: Empowers Earthshaker's totem, causing it to deal extra damage and have 75 bonus attack range on the next attack.

earthshaker_aftershock.desc: Causes the earth to shake underfoot, adding additional damage and stuns to nearby enemy units when Earthshaker casts his abilities.

earthshaker_echo_slam.desc: Shockwaves travel through the ground, damaging enemy units.  Each enemy hit causes an echo to damage nearby units. Real heroes cause two echoes.

juggernaut_blade_dance.desc: Gives Juggernaut a chance to deal critical damage on each attack.

juggernaut_blade_fury.desc:
Causes a bladestorm of destructive force around Juggernaut, rendering him immune to magic and dealing damage to nearby enemy units. 

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

juggernaut_healing_ward.desc: Summons a Healing Ward which heals all nearby allied units, based on their max health.  The Healing Ward moves at 350 movement speed after being summoned.  Lasts 25 seconds.

juggernaut_omni_slash.desc: Juggernaut leaps towards the target enemy units, and then slashes the target and other nearby enemy units at an increased attack rate. Juggernaut is invulnerable for the duration.

juggernaut_swift_slash.desc: Performs a mini Omnislash for a short duration.

kunkka_tidal_wave.desc: Releases a Tidal Wave that spawns behind Kunkka. Deals 250 damage and drags enemies along it for 600 distance. Enemies cannot attack while being dragged.

kunkka_torrent.desc: Summons a rising torrent that, after a short delay, hurls enemy units into the sky, stunning, dealing damage and slowing movement speed.

kunkka_torrent_storm.desc: Releases a visible Torrent in a random area around Kunkka once every 0.25 for 5 seconds. Spawns within 1100 range of him.

kunkka_tidebringer.desc: Kunkka's legendary sword grants increased damage and cleaves a large area of effect in front of him for a single strike.

kunkka_x_marks_the_spot.desc: Targets a friendly or enemy Hero, marks their position with an X, and returns them to it after several seconds.  Kunkka can trigger the return at any time during the duration. Lasts twice as long on allied heroes.

kunkka_return.desc: Returns the marked hero to the X.

kunkka_ghostship.desc: Summons a ghostly ship that sails through the battle before smashing apart, damaging and stunning all enemies caught near the wreckage. Allied heroes touched by the Ghostship are given a swig of The Admiral's Rum, receiving bonus movement speed and a delayed reaction to incoming damage.

lina_dragon_slave.desc: Lina channels the breath of a dragon, sending out a wave of fire that scorches every enemy in its path.

lina_light_strike_array.desc: Summons a column of flames that damages and stuns enemies.

lina_fiery_soul.desc: Grants bonus attack and movement speed each time Lina casts a spell. Stacks with itself. Lasts 12 seconds.

lina_laguna_blade.desc: Fires off a bolt of lightning at a single enemy unit, dealing massive damage.

lion_impale.desc: Rock spikes burst from the earth along a straight path. Enemy units are hurled into the air, then are stunned and take damage when they fall.

lion_voodoo.desc: Transforms an enemy unit into a harmless beast, with all special abilities disabled.

lion_mana_drain.desc: CHANNELED - Absorbs the magical energies of a target enemy unit by taking mana from it every second.

lion_finger_of_death.desc: Rips at an enemy unit, trying to turn it inside-out. Deals massive damage and grows stronger with each life it consumes.

mirana_arrow.desc: Fires a long-range arrow with deadly precision, which stuns and damages the first enemy unit it strikes. The stun duration ranges from 0.01 to 3.5,4,4.5,5 seconds, with bonus damage up to 180 added, based on the distance the arrow travels to its target. Instantly kills the first non-ancient creep it hits.

mirana_invis.desc: Turns Mirana and all allied heroes invisible and grants bonus movement speed. If a hero is revealed, invisibility will restore after the fade delay as long as Moonlight Shadow's duration has not expired.

mirana_leap.desc: Mirana leaps forward into battle, empowering herself with a ferocious roar that grants bonus attack and movement speed. Speed bonus lasts 2.5 seconds.

mirana_starfall.desc: Calls down a wave of meteors to damage nearby enemy units. The closest enemy unit to Mirana in a 425 radius will be struck a second time for 75% of the damage.

morphling_waveform.desc: Morphling dissolves into liquid and surges forward, damaging enemy units in his path.  Morphling is invulnerable during Waveform.

morphling_adaptive_strike_agi.desc:
Launches a surge of water toward an enemy unit, dealing base damage plus additional damage based on Morphling's agility times a multiplier.  If Morphling's agility is 50% higher than strength, the maximum agility multiplier is used. 

 Also puts Adaptive Strike (Strength) on a 3 second cooldown.

morphling_adaptive_strike_str.desc:
Launches a surge of water toward an enemy unit, stunning and knocking back the target based on Morphling's strength. If his strength is 50% higher than his agility, the maximum stun/knockback is dealt. 

 Also puts Adaptive Strike (Agility) on a 3 second cooldown.

morphling_morph_agi.desc: Morphling shifts its form, pulling points from Strength and pouring them into Agility. The process is reversible.  Additional points in Attribute Shift increase the rate of stat change.  Passively grants bonus Agility.

morphling_morph_str.desc: Morphling shifts its form, pulling points from Agility and pouring them into Strength. The process is reversible.  Additional points in Attribute Shift increase the rate of stat change.  Passively grants bonus Strength.

morphling_replicate.desc: Morphling changes his form to match the targeted enemy, gaining their basic abilities with reduced mana cost. Can be toggled for the duration of the ability.

morphling_morph_replicate.desc: Toggles Morphling's form between his own and the replicated enemy.

morphling_hybrid.desc: Morphling creates a hybrid replication of a target allied hero, which can cast all of that hero's current, non-ultimate abilities. Enemies are able to see which unit is a hybrid.

nevermore_shadowraze1.desc: Shadow Fiend razes the ground directly in front of him, dealing damage to enemy units in the area. Adds a stacking damage amplifier on the target that causes the enemy to take bonus Shadow Raze damage per stack.

nevermore_shadowraze2.desc: Shadow Fiend razes the ground a short distance away from him, dealing damage to enemy units in the area. Adds a stacking damage amplifier on the target that causes the enemy to take bonus Shadow Raze damage per stack.

nevermore_shadowraze3.desc: Shadow Fiend razes the ground a longer distance away from him, dealing damage to enemy units in the area. Adds a stacking damage amplifier on the target that causes the enemy to take bonus Shadow Raze damage per stack.

nevermore_necromastery.desc: Shadow Fiend steals the soul from units he kills, gaining bonus damage. On death, he releases 40% of them from bondage.

nevermore_dark_lord.desc: Shadow Fiend's presence reduces the armor of nearby enemies.

nevermore_requiem.desc: Shadow Fiend gathers his captured souls to release them as lines of demonic energy. Units near Shadow Fiend when the souls are released can be damaged by several lines of energy. Any unit damaged by Requiem of Souls will be feared and have its movement speed reduced for 0.8 seconds for each line hit. Lines of energy are created for every soul captured through Necromastery.  Requiem of Souls is automatically cast whenever Shadow Fiend dies, regardless of its cooldown.

phantom_lancer_spirit_lance.desc: Sends a magical spirit lance to a target enemy unit that damages and slows, while summoning an illusory phantom to attack the unit.

phantom_lancer_doppelwalk.desc:
Phantom Lancer briefly vanishes from the battlefield. After 1 second, Phantom Lancer and any of his nearby illusions reappear at a random position within the targeted location, along with two additional doppelgangers. Extends duration of all illusions. The two added doppelgangers have different properties: one takes normal damage and deals none, while the other takes 500% bonus damage and deals -80% less damage.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

phantom_lancer_juxtapose.desc: Phantom Lancer has a chance to fracture his presence, creating an illusion of himself. Illusions also have a chance to fracture further. Illusions created from Phantom Lancer last for 8 seconds, while illusions created from other illusions last 4 seconds.

phantom_lancer_phantom_edge.desc: When targetting an enemy for an attack, Phantom Lancer quickly charges into range, gaining a temporary agility boost. Phantom Lancer's illusions also have this ability.

puck_illusory_orb.desc: Puck launches a magic orb that floats in a straight path, damaging enemy units along the way. At any point, Puck may teleport to the orb's location using Ethereal Jaunt.

puck_ethereal_jaunt.desc: Teleports Puck to a flying Illusory Orb.

puck_waning_rift.desc: Puck teleports to the target location and releases a burst of faerie dust that deals damage and silences enemy units nearby.

puck_phase_shift.desc: CHANNELED - Puck briefly shifts into another dimension where it is immune from harm.

puck_dream_coil.desc: Creates a coil of volatile magic that latches onto enemy Heroes, stunning them for 0.5 seconds, damaging and leashing them.  If the enemy hero stretches the coil by moving too far away, it snaps, stunning and dealing additional damage.

pudge_flesh_heap.desc: Gives Pudge increased magic resistance, as well as bonus strength that increases each time Pudge kills an enemy Hero or it dies in his vicinity.  Flesh Heap is retroactive, meaning it can gain charges before it is skilled, which then become active.

pudge_meat_hook.desc: Launches a bloody hook toward a unit or location. The hook will snag the first unit it encounters, dragging the unit back to Pudge and dealing damage if it is an enemy.

pudge_rot.desc: A toxic cloud that deals intense damage and slows movement--harming not only enemy units but Pudge himself.

pudge_eject.desc: Ejects the swallowed allied hero inside of you.

pudge_dismember.desc: CHANNELED - Pudge chows down on an enemy unit, disabling it and dealing damage over time. Pudge gets healed for the same amount he damages. Lasts longer on creeps.

shadow_shaman_ether_shock.desc: Creates a cone of ethereal energy that strikes multiple enemy units.

shadow_shaman_voodoo.desc: Transforms an enemy unit into a harmless creature, disabling their attacks and abilities.

shadow_shaman_shackles.desc: CHANNELED - Magically binds an enemy unit so that it cannot move or attack, while dealing damage over time.

shadow_shaman_mass_serpent_ward.desc: Summons 10 Serpent Wards to attack enemy units and structures. The Wards are immune to magic.

shadow_shaman_serpentine.desc: Creates a line of 8 Serpent Wards.

razor_plasma_field.desc: Releases a wave of energetic plasma that grows in power as it expands, but also zaps on contraction, slowing and dealing damage to enemy units caught in its path. Damage and slow increases with distance from Razor. The Plasma Field hits each unit twice, once each direction.

razor_static_link.desc: Creates a charged link between Razor and an enemy Hero, stealing damage from the target and giving it to Razor. Allows razor to attack while moving with the link active.

razor_eye_of_the_storm.desc: A powerful lightning storm strikes out at enemy units with the lowest health, dealing damage and reducing their armor.

skeleton_king_hellfire_blast.desc: Wraith King sears an enemy unit with spectral fire, dealing damage and stunning, then dealing damage over time and slowing the target.

skeleton_king_vampiric_aura.desc: Restore health based on the damage Wraith King deals when attacking enemy units. Can be cast to summon skeletons with Vampiric Spirit. Every two kills on an enemy unit adds a skeleton charge. Skeletons respawn once when killed.

skeleton_king_mortal_strike.desc: Wraith King passively deals bonus damage on an attack with a cooldown.

skeleton_king_reincarnation.desc: Wraith King's form regroups after death, allowing him to resurrect when killed in battle.  Upon death, enemy units in a 900 radius will be slowed.

death_prophet_carrion_swarm.desc: Sends a swarm of winged beasts to savage enemy units in front of Death Prophet.

death_prophet_silence.desc: Prevents enemy units in a target area from casting spells.

death_prophet_spirit_siphon.desc: Creates a spirit link between Death Prophet and an enemy unit, draining 14 + 1,2.5,4,5.5% Max HP per second from the enemy.

death_prophet_exorcism.desc: Unleashes evil spirits to drain the life of nearby enemy units and structures. At the end of the spell's duration, Death Prophet is healed in proportion to the damage dealt. Lasts 35 seconds.

sven_storm_bolt.desc: Sven unleashes his magical gauntlet that deals damage and stuns enemy units in a small area around the target.

sven_great_cleave.desc: Sven strikes with great force, cleaving all nearby enemy units with his attack.

sven_warcry.desc: Sven's Warcry heartens his allied heroes for battle, increasing their armor and movement speed. Lasts 8 seconds.

sven_gods_strength.desc: Sven channels his rogue strength, granting bonus damage for 40 seconds.

storm_spirit_electric_rave.desc: Grants Storm Spirit and allied heroes within 750 AoE of him 3 Overload charges. Provides 40 Attack Speed. Lasts up to 12 seconds or until the charges are depleted.

storm_spirit_static_remnant.desc: Creates an explosively charged image of Storm Spirit that lasts 12 seconds and will detonate and deal damage if an enemy unit comes near it.

storm_spirit_electric_vortex.desc: A vortex that pulls an enemy unit to Storm Spirit's location.

storm_spirit_overload.desc: Casting a spell creates an electrical charge, which is released in a burst on Storm's next attack, dealing damage and slowing nearby enemies.

storm_spirit_ball_lightning.desc: Storm Spirit becomes volatile electricity, charging across the battlefield until he depletes his mana or reaches his target. The activation mana cost is 30+8% of his total mana pool, and the cost per 100 units traveled is 10+0.65% of his total mana pool.  Damage is expressed in damage per 100 units traveled.

sandking_burrowstrike.desc: Sand King burrows into the ground and tunnels forward, damaging and stunning enemy units above him as he resurfaces.

sandking_sand_storm.desc: Sand King creates a fearsome sandstorm that damages enemy units while hiding him from vision.  The effect ends when Sand King leaves the area.

sandking_caustic_finale.desc: Sand King's attacks inject a venom that causes enemy units to move more slowly and to violently explode when it dies.

sandking_epicenter.desc: CHANNELED - After channeling for %abilitychanneltime% seconds, Sand King sends a disturbance into the earth, causing it to shudder violently. All enemies caught within range will take damage and become slowed. Each subsequent pulse increases the radius of damage dealt.

tiny_avalanche.desc: Bombards an area with rocks, continously doing small intervals of damage and stun to enemy units. Avalanche does 2.5x damage to units being tossed.

tiny_toss.desc: Grabs the nearest unit in a 275 radius around Tiny, ally or enemy, and launches it at the target unit or rune to deal damage where they land.  If the tossed unit is an enemy, it will take an extra 30% damage.

tiny_craggy_exterior.desc: Enemies that attack Tiny have a 20% chance of being stunned for 1 second and taking 100 damage. Affects enemies within 400 range of him. Procs after an attack impacts, and does not affect spell immune enemies.

tiny_tree_grab.desc: Grabs a tree to whack enemies on the head for a limited number of attacks. Grants bonus attack range. Attacks deal more damage and fully splash on units along the way. The tree can be thrown, to deal your attack to a unit at a distance.

tiny_toss_tree.desc: Throws the tree at the target unit, proccing your attack on it and splashing damage around the target.

tiny_tree_channel.desc: Tiny channels this ability to throw random trees within range towards the targeted aoe. Deals Tiny's attack damage plus a bonus to enemies in that area with each tree thrown.

tiny_grow.desc: Tiny gains craggy mass, increasing his attack damage, and armor, while slowing his attack speed.

zuus_heavenly_jump.desc: Jumps forward a distance of 350 units. Midway through the jump a Arc Lightning is cast on a an enemy within its cast range.

zuus_arc_lightning.desc: Hurls a bolt of lightning that leaps through nearby enemy units.

zuus_lightning_bolt.desc: Calls down a bolt of lightning to strike an enemy unit, causing damage and a mini-stun. When cast, Lightning Bolt briefly provides unobstructed vision and True Sight around the target in a 750 radius. Can be cast on the ground, affecting the closest enemy hero in 325 range.

zuus_cloud.desc: Creates a storm cloud anywhere on the map that automatically casts Lightning Bolt on nearby enemies.

zuus_static_field.desc: Zeus shocks any enemy hit by his abilities, causing damage proportional to their current health.

zuus_thundergods_wrath.desc: Strikes all enemy heroes with a bolt of lightning, no matter where they may be.  Thundergod's Wrath also provides True Sight around each hero struck.  If an enemy hero is invisible, it takes no damage, but the True Sight is still created at that hero's location.

slardar_sprint.desc: Slardar slithers ahead, moving significantly faster and passing through units. Slardar gains movement speed bonus while in the river.

slardar_slithereen_crush.desc: Slams the ground, stunning and damaging nearby enemy land units.  After the stun, the affected units are slowed.

slardar_bash.desc: After 3 attacks, your next attack will bash the target. Deals double damage against creeps.

slardar_amplify_damage.desc: Reduces enemy armor to amplify physical damage and provides True Sight and vision of the targeted unit, revealing invisibility.

tidehunter_gush.desc: Summons a gush of water to damage an enemy unit, reducing their movement speed and armor.

tidehunter_kraken_shell.desc:
Thickens Tidehunter's hide to passively block a portion of any incoming physical attack damage. The hide also removes negative status effects if the damage taken crosses a threshold.

Does not stack with items that provide Damage Block.

DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

tidehunter_anchor_smash.desc: Tidehunter swings his mighty anchor to attack and deal bonus damage to nearby enemies and reduce their attack damage.

tidehunter_ravage.desc: Slams the ground, causing tentacles to erupt in all directions, damaging and stunning all nearby enemy units.

vengefulspirit_magic_missile.desc: Fires a magic missile at an enemy unit, stunning and dealing damage.

vengefulspirit_command_aura.desc: Vengeful Spirit's presence increases the damage of nearby friendly heroes.

vengefulspirit_wave_of_terror.desc: Vengeful Spirit lets loose a wicked cry, weakening the armor of enemies and giving vision of the path ahead.

vengefulspirit_nether_swap.desc: Instantaneously swaps positions with a target Hero, friend or enemy.  Nether Swap interrupts channeling abilities on the target.

crystal_maiden_let_it_go.desc: Creates an icy path towards the targeted direction, allowing you to move faster and path freely. Enemies walking over this path will move slower.

crystal_maiden_crystal_nova.desc: A burst of damaging frost slows enemy movement and attack rate in the targeted area.

crystal_maiden_frostbite.desc: Encases an enemy unit in ice, prohibiting movement and attack, while dealing damage over time. Lasts 10 seconds on creeps level 6 or lower.

crystal_maiden_brilliance_aura.desc: Gives additional mana regeneration to all friendly units on the map. This bonus is increased for Crystal Maiden.

crystal_maiden_freezing_field.desc: CHANNELED - Surrounds Crystal Maiden with random icy explosions that slow enemies and deal massive damage. Grants bonus armor while channeling. Lasts 10 seconds.

windrunner_shackleshot.desc: Shackles the target to an enemy unit or tree in a line directly behind it.  If no unit or tree is present, the stun duration is reduced to 0.75,0.75,0.75,0.75.

windrunner_powershot.desc: Windranger charges her bow for up to 1 second for a single powerful shot, which deals more damage the longer it is charged. The arrow damages enemies along its path. For each enemy that Powershot hits, its damage is reduced by 20%.

windrunner_windrun.desc: Increases movement speed and adds evasion from all physical attacks, while slowing movement of nearby enemies.

windrunner_focusfire.desc: Windranger channels the wind to gain 475 additional attack speed against a single enemy unit or structure, though with a reduction to her attack damage.  Extra damage from secondary item effects is not reduced.

lich_frost_nova.desc: Blasts the target enemy unit with damaging frost, dealing area damage and slowing movement and attack rates for 4 seconds.  The primary target receives both base and area damage.

lich_dark_sorcery.desc: Grants you bonus attack speed for a limited number of attacks, draining a percentage of mana for each hit. Costs a percentage of current health to cast. Lasts up to 15 seconds or when the attack count is consumed.

lich_sinister_gaze.desc: CHANNELED - Hypnotizes an enemy unit, causing it to move towards a point between the two of you and drains a percentage of its current mana.

lich_frost_aura.desc: Allied Aura. Causes all nearby ally attacks to slow enemy movement speed.

lich_frost_armor.desc: Creates a shield around the target friendly unit or building, which adds armor and slows attacking units. Lasts 40 seconds.

lich_frost_shield.desc: Applies a magical frost shield around the target, reducing damage from attacks against you. While the shield is active, ice magic will affect nearby enemy units every 1 seconds, dealing minor damage and slowing them.

lich_chain_frost.desc: Releases an orb of frost that bounces between nearby enemy units up to 10,10,10 times, slowing and damaging each time it hits. Each bounce increases the damage for the subsequent bounces.

lich_ice_spire.desc: Creates an icicle at the target spot for 15 seconds, slowing enemies within 750 range by -30%. Has 800 health.Chain Frost can bounce to the Icicle if there are no other enemies in range.Can cast Frost Shield on it.

witch_doctor_paralyzing_cask.desc: Launches a cask of paralyzing powder that ricochets between enemy units, stunning and damaging those it hits.

witch_doctor_voodoo_restoration.desc: Witch Doctor focuses his magic to heal nearby allied units, costing Witch Doctor mana every second Voodoo restoration is active.

witch_doctor_maledict.desc: Curses all enemy Heroes in a small area, causing them to take a set amount of damage each second, as well as bursts of damage every 4 seconds based on how much health they have lost since the curse began.

witch_doctor_death_ward.desc: CHANNELED - Summons a deadly ward to attack enemy heroes within it's attack range. Lasts a maximum of 8 seconds.

witch_doctor_voodoo_switcheroo.desc: Turns Witch Doctor into a Death Ward for 2 seconds. Death Ward has -30 Attack Speed. He is hidden during this time.

riki_poison_dart.desc: Fires a dart at the target enemy, putting them to sleep for 4 seconds or if they take 200 damage. At the end of the duration, the target wakes up and takes 150 damage, and is slowed by 30% for 4 seconds.

riki_smoke_screen.desc: Throws down a smoke bomb, silencing enemies, and causing them to miss attacks.

riki_blink_strike.desc: Teleports behind the target unit, striking for bonus damage if it is an enemy.

riki_backstab.desc: Riki fades into the shadows, becoming invisible. Every time Riki strikes his enemy from behind, he deals bonus damage based on his Agility. When Riki attacks, he becomes visible.

riki_permanent_invisibility.desc: Riki fades into the shadows, becoming invisible. When Riki attacks, he becomes visible. Grants bonus movement speed

riki_tricks_of_the_trade.desc: Riki phases out of the world while striking random enemy units from behind in an area around him.

enigma_malefice.desc: Focuses Enigma's power on a target, causing it to take damage and become repeatedly stunned for multiple instances.  An instance strikes every 2,2,2,2 seconds.

enigma_demonic_conversion.desc: Transforms a creep into three fragments of Enigma himself.  These eidolons are all under Enigma's control, and repeated successful attacks cause them to multiply.  When this happens, the eidolons have their health restored.

enigma_midnight_pulse.desc: Steeps an area in dark resonance, damaging enemy units based on their max HP.

enigma_black_hole.desc: CHANNELED - Summons a vortex that sucks in nearby enemy units.  Enemies affected by Black Hole cannot move, attack, or cast spells.

tinker_defense_matrix.desc: Targets an allied unit, applying a barrier to them that blocks the next 350 damage and provides 50% Status Resistance. Barrier lasts up to 15 seconds.

tinker_laser.desc: Fires an intense energy beam, dealing damage and blinding the target, causing it to miss all physical attacks.

tinker_shrink_ray.desc: Reduces the enemy target size and lowers their max health by 20% for 6 seconds.

tinker_heat_seeking_missile.desc: Launches rockets at the nearest visible enemy heroes within 2500,2500,2500,2500 range.

tinker_march_of_the_machines.desc: Enlists an army of robotic minions to destroy enemy units in an area around Tinker.

tinker_rearm.desc: CHANNELED - Resets the cooldown on most of Tinker's items and abilities.

sniper_concussive_grenade.desc: Grants Concussive Grenade. Deals 125 damage, knocking enemies back 425 distance, slowing them by 50% and disarming them for 3 seconds. Radius: 375. Knocks you back 450 units on cast.

sniper_shrapnel.desc: Consumes a charge to launch a ball of shrapnel that showers the target area in explosive pellets. Enemies are subject to damage and slowed movement. Reveals the targeted area. Shrapnel charges restore every 35 seconds.

sniper_headshot.desc: Sniper increases his accuracy, giving him a chance to deal extra damage and briefly knocks back his enemies.

sniper_take_aim.desc: Extends the attack range of Sniper's rifle. Can be activated to provided True Strike and +30% Headshot chance for 4 seconds. Slows you by 30% for the duration.

sniper_assassinate.desc: Sniper locks onto a target enemy unit and, after a short aiming duration, fires a devastating shot that deals damage at long range and mini-stuns the target.

necrolyte_death_seeker.desc: Spawns a fast moving large Death Pulse towards the target enemy or ally, causing the target to become ethereal for 2.5 seconds. Reduces enemy magic resistance by 25%. Spreads towards nearby enemies and allies after impact.

necrolyte_death_pulse.desc: Necrophos releases a wave of death around him, dealing damage to enemy units and healing allied units.

necrolyte_heartstopper_aura.desc: Necrophos stills the hearts of his opponents, causing nearby enemy units to lose a percentage of their max health over time. Passively provides regen for 8 seconds for each unit Necrophos kills.

necrolyte_sadist.desc: Necrophos slips into the realm that separates the living from the dead. Unable to attack or be attacked, he emits an aura that slows enemies around him. He takes additional magic damage in this form, but his restorative powers are amplified.

necrolyte_reapers_scythe.desc: Stuns the target enemy hero, then deals damage based on how much life it is missing. Heroes killed by Reaper's Scythe will have 15,25,35 seconds added to their respawn timer. Any kill under this effect is credited to Necrophos.

warlock_fatal_bonds.desc: Binds several enemy units together, causing a percentage of the damage dealt to one of them to be felt by the others.

warlock_shadow_word.desc: Warlock whispers an incantation, healing a friendly unit or damaging an enemy unit over time.

warlock_upheaval.desc: CHANNELED - A powerful slowing current that grows stronger as it's channelled. Lasts up to 10,12,14,16 seconds.  Enemies are slowed for 3 seconds after leaving the area or the spell ends.

warlock_rain_of_chaos.desc: Summons a Golem from the depths, stunning enemies for one second. The Golem lives 60,60,60 seconds, takes reduced damage from spells, has Permanent Immolation and Flaming Fists on attack.

warlock_golem_flaming_fists.desc: Deals extra damage to nearby units when attacking.

warlock_golem_permanent_immolation.desc: Burns the Golem's nearby enemy units, with damage per second.

beastmaster_wild_axes.desc: Beastmaster sends his axes flying and calls them home again, slicing through enemy units and trees along their path.  Each axe can hit an enemy once, and amplifies subsequent damage from Beastmaster and his units.

beastmaster_call_of_the_wild_boar.desc: Beastmaster calls forth a Boar to aid in the battlefield.

beastmaster_hawk_dive.desc: Reveals itself for 1, and then flies towards the target enemy, dealing 250 damage and stunning them for 2 second, killing the hawk.

beastmaster_call_of_the_wild_hawk.desc: Beastmaster sends an invisible Hawk to scout an area.

beastmaster_hawk_invisibility.desc: If motionless for some time, the hawk becomes invisible.

beastmaster_boar_poison.desc: Inflicts a poison that slows attack and movement speeds.

beastmaster_greater_boar_poison.desc: Inflicts a poison that slows attack and movement speeds.

beastmaster_inner_beast.desc: Untaps the inner fury of nearby allies, passively increasing their attack speed.

beastmaster_primal_roar.desc: Beastmaster lets loose a deafening roar that stuns, and shoves open a path to its target. All units in the path of the roar are damaged, while units shoved aside by the roar have their movement and attack speed slowed. Additionally, Beastmaster and his units gain 40% movement speed for 3 seconds.

queenofpain_shadow_strike.desc: Hurls a poisoned dagger which deals large initial damage, and then deals damage over time. The poisoned unit has its movement speed slowed for 15 seconds.  An instance of damage is dealt every 3 seconds.

queenofpain_blink.desc: Short distance teleportation that allows Queen of Pain to move in and out of combat.

queenofpain_scream_of_pain.desc: The Queen of Pain lets loose a piercing scream around her, damaging nearby enemies.

queenofpain_sonic_wave.desc: Creates a gigantic wave of sound in front of Queen of Pain, dealing heavy damage to all enemy units in its wake and pushing them back.

venomancer_area_poison.desc: Creates a 650 AoE pool of poison at the target location, dealing another instance of Poison Nova damage and slows by 20%. If an enemy dies in the area, a Plague Ward is spawned.

venomancer_venomous_gale.desc: Launches a ball of venom in a line, poisoning enemy units so that they take both initial damage and damage over time, as well as suffering slowed movement.  Venomous Gale deals damage every 3 seconds over its duration.

venomancer_poison_sting.desc: Adds poison damage to Venomancer's normal attacks and slowing movement speed.

venomancer_plague_ward.desc: Summons a plague ward to attack enemy units and structures. The ward is immune to magic. Wards gain the Poison Sting level from Venomancer, dealing 50% of the full damage.

venomancer_poison_nova.desc: A spreading ring of poison that does damage over time to enemy units around Venomancer.  Poison Nova cannot deal lethal damage; targets will be left with at least 1 health.

faceless_void_time_walk.desc: Rushes to a target location while backtracking any damage taken the last 2 seconds.

faceless_void_time_walk_reverse.desc: Replaces Time Walk with Reverse Time Walk for 1.5 seconds after landing. If used in this period, you will reverse your time walk back to your previous cast location. Does not affect health or proc scepter hits.

faceless_void_time_lock.desc: Adds the chance for an attack to lock an enemy unit in time while attacking it a second time.

faceless_void_time_dilation.desc: Faceless Void traps all nearby enemies in a time dilation field for 8,9,10,11 seconds, extending their cooldowns and slowing their movement and attack speed by 10% for each cooldown extended. Deals damage per second for each cooldown.

faceless_void_chronosphere.desc: Creates a blister in spacetime, trapping all units caught in its sphere of influence and causes you to move very quickly inside it.  Only Faceless Void and any units he controls are unaffected.  Invisible enemies in the sphere will be revealed.

pugna_nether_blast.desc: An exploding pulse deals damage to enemies and structures in the area.  Deals half damage to structures.

pugna_decrepify.desc: A powerful banishing spell that slows a unit and renders it unable to attack or be attacked. Afflicted units take extra magic damage.

pugna_nether_ward.desc: Pugna places a Nether Ward at the target location. The ward causes nearby enemy heroes to lose a percentage of their max mana every second, and will fire at any enemy hero who casts a spell. Nether Ward deals base damage plus the damage multiplier of the mana spent by the enemy hero.

pugna_life_drain.desc:
CHANNELED - When cast on an enemy, Pugna drains health from the target enemy unit to heal himself and granting vision over the target. If Pugna has full HP, and the enemy target is a Hero, Life Drain will restore mana instead.

When cast on an ally, Pugna will drain his own health into his ally.

phantom_assassin_fan_of_knives.desc: Phantom Assassin releases sharp blades around her in a 550 AoE, dealing 16% of a victim's max health on impact and applying break for 3 seconds.

phantom_assassin_stifling_dagger.desc: Throws a dagger slowing the enemy unit's movement speed, dealing 65+25,40,55,70% of Phantom Assassin's attack damage as physical damage and applying attack effects from items and abilities.

phantom_assassin_phantom_strike.desc: Teleports to a unit, friendly or enemy, and grants bonus attack speed while attacking if it's an enemy unit.

phantom_assassin_blur.desc:
Phantom Assassin focuses inward, increasing her ability to evade enemy attacks. Can be activated to blur her body, causing her to be impossible to see until near enemy heroes.

Stacks diminishingly with other sources of Evasion.

phantom_assassin_coup_de_grace.desc: Phantom Assassin refines her combat abilities, gaining a chance of delivering a devastating critical strike to enemy units. Stifling Dagger shares the same critical strike chance.

templar_assassin_refraction.desc: Templar Assassin becomes highly elusive, avoiding damage and gaining a bonus to her damage.  The damage and avoidance effects are separate, and have a limited number of instances.

templar_assassin_meld.desc: Templar Assassin conceals herself, becoming invisible as long as she remains still.  If Meld's invisibility is broken by attacking an enemy, Lanaya will deal bonus damage to the enemy and reduce their armor for 12 seconds.

templar_assassin_psi_blades.desc: Templar Assassin's psi blades slice through the attacked unit, splitting and damaging enemy units directly behind it, while gaining bonus attack range.

templar_assassin_psionic_trap.desc: Templar Assassin places mystical traps that invisibly monitor enemy movement. When sprung at her command, they exert a slowing influence of 30% in the area. Traps charge up to slow 60% after 4 seconds. Deals bonus damage when fully charged.

templar_assassin_trap.desc: Springs the nearest trap, slowing nearby enemies.

templar_assassin_trap_teleport.desc: Allows Templar Assassin to teleport to any Psionic Trap after a brief channel. Does not break meld. Detonates the Psionic Trap on arrival.

templar_assassin_self_trap.desc: Springs the trap, slowing nearby enemies.

viper_poison_attack.desc: Intensifies Viper's venom, adding an effect to his normal attack that applies a stacking movement speed slow and magic resistance deduction while dealing damage over time. Stacks up to 5 times.

viper_nethertoxin.desc: Viper releases a Nethertoxin at the targeted area. Units in that area take an increasing damage over time based on how long they remain in it. Disables passives of affected units.

viper_corrosive_skin.desc: Viper exudes an infectious toxin that damages and slows the attack speed of any enemy that damages it in a 1400 radius. The acid exudate also increases Viper's resistance to magic.

viper_viper_strike.desc: Viper slows the targeted enemy unit's movement and attack speed while also dealing poison damage over time.  The slowing effect reduces over the duration of the poison.

luna_lucent_beam.desc: Calls a beam of lunar energy down upon an enemy, damaging and briefly stunning them.

luna_moon_glaive.desc: Empowers Luna's glaives, causing her attacks to bounce between enemy units. Deals less damage with each bounce.

luna_lunar_blessing.desc: Increases the attack damage for Luna and nearby allied heroes. Luna is also blessed with increased vision range at night.

luna_lunar_grace.desc: Dispels negative buffs and grants you bonus attack speed. Has an increased effect during the night.

luna_eclipse.desc: Showers random nearby enemies with strikes from Luna's current level of Lucent Beam. These beams do not stun their targets, and there is a maximum number of times that a single target can be struck. Also turns day into night for 10 seconds.

dragon_knight_fireball.desc: Ignites a 450 AoE area for 10 seconds, dealing 80 damage per second to enemies in it. Has reduced cast range when melee.

dragon_knight_breathe_fire.desc: Unleashes a breath of fire in front of Dragon Knight that burns enemies and reduces the damage their attacks deal.

dragon_knight_dragon_tail.desc: Dragon Knight smites an enemy unit in melee range with his shield, stunning it while dealing minor damage.  When in Elder Dragon Form, the cast range increases to 400.

dragon_knight_dragon_blood.desc: The life blood of the Dragon improves health regeneration and strengthens armor.

dragon_knight_elder_dragon_form.desc:
Dragon Knight takes the form of one of three powerful elder dragons, increasing his speed, and Dragon Tail's range, while granting him new powers.
LEVEL 1 Green Dragon - Corrosive Breath: attacks deal 20,20,20,30 poison damage per second for 5,5,5 seconds. Works on structures.
LEVEL 2 Red Dragon - Splash Attack: attacks damage all enemy units in a 350 radius for 75,75,75,115% damage, with Corrosive Breath added to the targets.
LEVEL 3 Blue Dragon - Frost Breath: slows movement speed by -40,-40,-40,-60% and attack speed by -40,-40,-40,-60 of enemy units in Splash Attack range for 3,3,3 seconds, with Corrosive Breath added to the targets.

dazzle_poison_touch.desc: Releases a cone of poison that strikes multiple enemy units. Deals damage over time and slows the targets. Anytime the targets get attacked, the debuff duration is refreshed.

dazzle_shallow_grave.desc: An ally blessed with Shallow Grave, no matter how close to death, cannot die while under its protection.

dazzle_shadow_wave.desc: Sends out a bolt of power that arcs between allies, healing them while damaging any units standing nearby.  Dazzle is always healed by Shadow Wave.

dazzle_weave.desc: Applies a buff that increases the armor of allied heroes while decreasing the armor of enemy heroes in the target area over time.

dazzle_bad_juju.desc: Passively reduces cooldowns on Dazzle's abilities and items. Anytime he casts a spell, all nearby enemies will have their armor reduced. Debuff stacks and refreshes duration.

rattletrap_jetpack.desc: Rises up, granting Clockwerk flying vision, flying movement, and a 20% bonus movement speed. Clockwerk has a severely-limited turn rate during this time and cannot attack. Lasts up to 6 seconds or until he casts Hookshot.

rattletrap_overclocking.desc: Resets Clockwerk's ability cooldowns and grants him bonus movement and attack speed for a duration. Clockwerk becomes stunned after the duration runs out.

rattletrap_battery_assault.desc: Discharges high-powered shrapnel at random nearby enemy units, dealing minor magical damage and ministun.

rattletrap_power_cogs.desc: Forms a barrier of energized cogs around Clockwerk, trapping any units that are near.  Enemies outside the trap that touch a cog are knocked back, losing health and mana. Once a cog has delivered a shock, it will power down.  Cogs can be destroyed by enemy attacks, but Clockwerk can destroy them with just one.

rattletrap_rocket_flare.desc: Fires a global range flare that explodes over a given area, damaging enemies and providing vision for 6 seconds.

rattletrap_hookshot.desc: Fires a grappling device rapidly at the target location.  If the hook hits a unit, Clockwerk launches himself into the target, stunning and dealing damage.  Any enemies Clockwerk collides with along the way are damaged and stunned.

leshrac_split_earth.desc: Splits the earth under enemies. Deals damage and stuns for a short duration.

leshrac_diabolic_edict.desc: Saturates the area around Leshrac with magical explosions that deal physical damage to enemy units and structures.  The fewer units available to attack, the more damage those units will take.  Deals 40% more damage to towers.  Lasts 10 seconds.

leshrac_lightning_storm.desc: Summons a lightning storm that blasts the target enemy unit, then strikes any nearby enemy units. Struck enemies are slowed.

leshrac_greater_lightning_storm.desc: Causes all nearby enemies in 450 AoE to turn ethereal, preventing them from attacking, causing them to take 30% more magic damage and be slowed by 30% for 4 seconds. Increases Leshrac's speed rather than reducing it. Does not cause you to take amplified damage.

leshrac_pulse_nova.desc: Creates waves of damaging energy around Leshrac, one per second, to damage nearby enemy units. Drains Leshrac's mana with each pulse.

furion_sprout.desc: Sprouts a ring of trees around a unit, trapping it in place, and providing vision in a 500 radius.

furion_greater_sprout.desc: Creates a larger circle of trees in a 300 AoE for 6 seconds. Ensnares enemies inside for 2 seconds, dealing 150 damage per second.

furion_teleportation.desc: Teleports to any point on the map.

furion_force_of_nature.desc: Converts an area of trees into Treants under the command of Nature's Prophet.

furion_wrath_of_nature.desc: Damaging energy bounces around the map, striking enemies close to the cast point that are in vision. Each enemy hit beyond the first adds damage. Enemies that die under this spell grant you bonus damage for 50 seconds.

life_stealer_rage.desc:
Launch into a maddened rage, becoming Spell Immune, and gaining increased movement speed.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

life_stealer_feast.desc: Lifestealer's attacks deal damage and provide heal for a percentage of his target's max health.

life_stealer_open_wounds.desc: Lifestealer rends an enemy unit, slowing the victim's movement speed and allowing all allies to regain health for a percentage of the damage they deal to that unit. All damage dealt will steal life, including damage from spells. The victim recovers movement speed over the duration. Deals 2% of the target's max health per attack on the target from real heroes.

life_stealer_ghoul_frenzy.desc: Passively causes Lifestealer's attacks to significantly slow enemy movement speed for 1.5 seconds. Grants you Attack Speed.

life_stealer_infest.desc:
Lifestealer infests the body of a target unit, becoming undetectable, and healing for a portion of his max hitpoints every second while inside. He can then explode from the host body, dealing damage to nearby enemies. If the infested unit is an enemy creep or a neutral creep, he can take control of the unit's ability to move and attack. Does not work on enemy heroes.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

life_stealer_assimilate.desc:
Lifestealer swallows an allied hero, allowing them to hide within him. Any healing Lifestealer receives is shared with the hero within. When an assimilated hero leaves Lifestealer, they erupt outward, damaging nearby enemies.

DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

life_stealer_assimilate_eject.desc: Ejects an Assimilated hero, damaging nearby enemies.

life_stealer_consume.desc: Lifestealer eats the host body from the inside out, exploding from within.

life_stealer_control.desc: Lifestealer seizes control of the host body's nervous system, allowing him to issue movement and attack orders from within.  Controlled units share Lifestealer's movement speed.  Cannot be used on heroes.

dark_seer_normal_punch.desc: Grants Normal Punch. Passive cooldown attack. Causes Dark Seer's next attack on a hero to knock an illusion out of the victim and stun them for up to 2.25 seconds, 350 distance and 250 damage based on how far Dark Seer has moved in the past 3 seconds. Max power is reached after 900 distance moved. Illusions lasts for 5 seconds. Cooldown: 14

dark_seer_vacuum.desc: Dark Seer creates a vacuum over the target area that sucks in enemy units, disrupting them and dealing damage.

dark_seer_ion_shell.desc: Surrounds the target unit with a bristling shield that damages enemy units in an area around it.

dark_seer_surge.desc: Charges a target friendly unit with power, giving it a brief burst of movement speed and removes unit collisions. Allows the unit to reach maximum movement speed and cannot be slowed.

dark_seer_wall_of_replica.desc: Raises a wall of warping light that slows and creates replicas of any enemy hero who crosses it. Enemy replicas serve at the Dark Seer's will. Replicas last until they are destroyed, or until the wall's duration ends.

clinkz_strafe.desc: Clinkz nimbly attacks with a barrage of arrows. Gains 100% evasion from ranged attackers and dramatically increases attack speed for a short time.

clinkz_searing_arrows.desc: Imbues Clinkz's arrows with fire for extra damage.

clinkz_wind_walk.desc: Clinkz moves invisibly through units until the moment he attacks or uses items.

clinkz_burning_army.desc: Clinkz summons an army of fiery ranged skeleton archers. Archers are immobile and die with 2 attacks from a hero. Skeletons deal a percentage of Clinkz' damage, use his current Searing Arrows ability and attack only heroes. Attack range is equal to Clinkz's attack range.

clinkz_death_pact.desc: Clinkz consumes the target enemy unit or friendly unit, gaining max health and damage based on its current health.

omniknight_hammer_of_purity.desc: Causes Omniknight's next attack to deal bonus pure damage based on 60 plus 115% of his base damage. He is healed for the same amount of pure damage. Cooldown: 4

omniknight_purification.desc: Instantly heals a friendly unit and damages all nearby enemy units.

omniknight_repel.desc:
Creates a divine barrier around an ally which grants them increased Status Resistance, Strength and Health Regeneration.

DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

omniknight_pacify.desc: Causes affected enemies to deal less spell damage for a duration.

omniknight_degen_aura.desc: Greatly degenerates the movement capabilities of enemy units that stray too near.

omniknight_guardian_angel.desc: Omniknight calls upon a Guardian Angel that grants allies immunity from physical damage.

enchantress_untouchable.desc: Enchantress beguiles her enemies, slowing their attacks when she is attacked.

enchantress_bunny_hop.desc: Leaps backward, dodges incoming projectiles, and launches an Impetus attack on the 3 furthest enemy units within Enchantress' attack range + 200.

enchantress_enchant.desc:
Enchantress charms an enemy. If the enemy is a hero, they are slowed. If the enemy is a creep, she brings it under her control, increasing it's attack damage and max health.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

enchantress_natures_attendants.desc: A cloud of wisps heals Enchantress and any friendly units nearby. Lasts 12 seconds.

enchantress_impetus.desc: Places an enchantment on each attack while activated, causing it to deal additional damage based on how far away the target is.  The farther the target, the greater the damage dealt.

huskar_inner_vitality.desc: Unlocks the regenerative power of a friendly unit, with healing based upon its primary attribute. If the target is below 35%, it will heal faster.  Lasts 16,16,16,16 seconds.

huskar_inner_fire.desc: In a fiery rage, knocks all nearby enemies away from you to a fixed distance, dealing damage and disarming them.

huskar_burning_spear.desc: Huskar sets his spears aflame, dealing damage over time with his regular attack.  Multiple attacks will stack additional damage.  Each attack drains some of Huskar's health.  Lasts 8 seconds.

huskar_berserkers_blood.desc: Huskar's injuries feed his power, giving increased attack speed and health regen based on missing health. Health regen is a percentage of your strength.

huskar_life_break.desc:
Huskar draws upon his health to break an enemy's life, leaping at a target within attack range to shatter a percentage of that hero's current health, and slowing them.  While leaping, Huskar is Spell Immune.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

night_stalker_void.desc: Creates a damaging void that slows an enemy unit and deals damage.  Void also mini-stuns, interrupting channeling abilities. The slowing effect lasts longer at night.

night_stalker_crippling_fear.desc: Night Stalker horrifies all nearby enemies, causing them to become silenced while near him.  The effect lasts longer at night.

night_stalker_hunter_in_the_night.desc: Night Stalker is in his element at night, attacking and moving with great swiftness.

night_stalker_darkness.desc: Night Stalker smothers the sun and summons instant darkness, so that he might use his powers at their fullest. Nightstalker gains flight and bonus damage during this time. Has unobstructed vision.

broodmother_spawn_spiderlings.desc: Broodmother injects her young into an enemy unit, dealing damage. The spiderlings will hatch if the target is killed while under this influence.

broodmother_poison_sting.desc: Poisons and slows enemies with each attack.

broodmother_spawn_spiderite.desc: Applies debuff on attack. If debuffed unit dies, a spiderite will spawn.

broodmother_spin_web.desc: Spins a large web that grants Broodmother a passive movement speed increase, gives free movement, and boosts regeneration while in its vicinity. Spin Web charges restore every 40 seconds. Spin Web can be cast from anywhere as long as the new web touches an existing web. Webs never expire, and can be manually destroyed. When the maximum limit of webs is exceeded, the oldest web disappears.

broodmother_silken_bola.desc: Slows the target enemy, causes them to miss and deals impact damage. Units that attack the target deal bonus magic damage.

broodmother_incapacitating_bite.desc: Broodmother's venom cripples enemy units, causing her attacks to slow and giving the affected unit a chance to miss its attacks.

broodmother_insatiable_hunger.desc: A violent lust for vital fluids increases Broodmother's attack damage and gives her a vampiric attack.

bounty_hunter_shuriken_toss.desc: Hurls a deadly shuriken at an enemy unit, dealing damage and mini-stunning the target.  The shuriken will bounce to any Tracked units who are within a 1200 radius of each other.

bounty_hunter_jinada.desc: Bounty Hunter plans his next hit, dealing bonus damage and stealing some unreliable gold.

bounty_hunter_wind_walk.desc: Bounty Hunter becomes invisible and gains the ability to move through other units until he attacks or uses an ability.  If he breaks the invisibility with an attack, that attack will slow the target's movement speed.

bounty_hunter_track.desc: Tracks an enemy hero, granting True Sight of the target, and information on how much gold it is carrying. Bounty Hunter moves fast when near the tracked unit and deals critical strikes when attacking it. If the target dies, Bounty Hunter and nearby heroes collect a bonus bounty of gold. Casting Track does not take you out of invisibility.

weaver_the_swarm.desc: Weaver launches a swarm of 12,12,12,12 young Weavers that latch on any enemy unit in their path, attacking and reducing armor until it is killed.

weaver_shukuchi.desc: Weaver shifts out of visibility, gaining max movement speed --doing harm to any enemies it passes through.

weaver_geminate_attack.desc: Allows Weaver to dispatch two attacks at once.

weaver_time_lapse.desc:
Weaver warps backward to whatever position it was in five seconds earlier--regaining the HP and mana from that time. No effect on cooldown, gold or experience.

DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

jakiro_dual_breath.desc: An icy blast followed by a wave of fire launches out in a path in front of Jakiro. The ice slows enemies, while the fire delivers damage over time.

jakiro_ice_path.desc: Creates a path of ice that stuns and damages enemies that touch it.

jakiro_liquid_fire.desc: Jakiro burns his enemies in an area of effect with fire added to his attack, while slowing their attacks.

jakiro_liquid_ice.desc: Stuns enemies for 0.4 seconds and applies a frost debuff that slows enemy movement speed by 20% and take 20 plus 2.5% of their max health per second as damage for 4 seconds.

jakiro_macropyre.desc: Jakiro exhales a wide line of lasting flames, which deals damage per second to any enemy units caught in the fire.

batrider_sticky_napalm.desc: Drenches an area in sticky oil, amplifying damage from Batrider's attacks and abilities and slowing the movement speed and turn rate of enemies in the area.  Additional casts of Sticky Napalm continue to increase damage, up to 10,10,10,10 stacks.

batrider_flamebreak.desc: Hurls an explosive cocktail that explodes when it reaches the target location, knocking back, and dealing damage over time to enemies in the area.

batrider_firefly.desc: Batrider takes to the skies, laying down a trail of flames from the air.  The fire damages any enemies it touches, and destroys trees below Batrider. Batrider has bonus day/night vision while Firefly is active.

batrider_flaming_lasso.desc: Lassoes an enemy and drags them in Batrider's wake.  Victims cannot be dragged over impassable terrain. Dragged units cannot move, attack, or use abilities.  Teleporting or blinking will break the lasso.

chen_penitence.desc: Forces an enemy unit to move slower and for allies to attack it more quickly.

chen_test_of_faith.desc: Deals random damage to test an enemy unit's faith. Heals a random amount to allied units. Always applies the maximum effect when cast on yourself.

chen_divine_favor.desc: Passively provides an aura that grants increased health regeneration and amplifies all health restore by a percentage.

chen_test_of_faith_teleport.desc: Teleports an allied unit back to the base.  Creeps are teleported instantly, while Heroes have a delay before teleporting. If cast on Chen, all units controlled by Chen through Holy Persuasion will be teleported to him after a delay.

chen_holy_persuasion.desc:
Chen takes control of an enemy or neutral creep. If the persuaded creep's base health is naturally below the health minimum, its base health will be raised to the health minimum. Converted creeps will have increased movement speed and bonus damage. 

Can be cast on converted creeps to teleport them to Chen. If cast on Chen, all units controlled by Chen will be teleported to him. Taking damage will dispel the buff.

chen_hand_of_god.desc: Heals all allied heroes on the map as well as all units under Chen's control.

spectre_spectral_dagger.desc: Spectre flings a dagger to draw a Shadow Path, dealing damage and slowing the movement speed of any enemies along the trail. Units hit by the dagger also trail a Shadow Path. While treading the path, Spectre phases through otherwise impassable terrain.

spectre_desolate.desc: Deals bonus damage whenever Spectre attacks an enemy that does not have any allied units within a 425 radius around them.

spectre_dispersion.desc: Damage done to Spectre is reflected on her enemies, leaving her unharmed. The effect lessens with distance.

spectre_haunt.desc:
Creates a spectral nemesis to attack each enemy hero. At any moment during the duration, Spectre can use Reality to exchange places of a given haunt.

Haunt illusions are uncontrollable, take extra damage, and deal less damage than Spectre herself.  They ignore terrain.

spectre_haunt_single.desc: Allows Spectre to perform a single target unit Haunt. Casts a Spectral Dagger on the target.

spectre_reality.desc: Spectre exchanges places with a chosen Haunt.

doom_bringer_devour.desc: Consumes an enemy or neutral creep, acquiring any special abilities that it possessed. If autocast is deactivated, Doom will not acquire the creep's abilities. Duration is equal to the cooldown.

doom_bringer_scorched_earth.desc: Carpets the nearby earth in flames which damage enemies, while also granting him increased movement speed.

doom_bringer_infernal_blade.desc: Doom swings his burning sword, igniting the enemy. Stuns for 0.6 seconds and applies a 4 second burn that deals a base damage plus a percentage of the target's Max HP as damage per second.

doom_bringer_doom.desc:
Inflicts a curse that dispels an enemy Hero and prevents an them from casting spells or using items, while taking damage over time.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

doom_bringer_empty1.desc: This slot will be replaced with abilities acquired using Devour.

doom_bringer_empty2.desc: This slot will be replaced with abilities acquired using Devour.

ancient_apparition_cold_feet.desc: Places a frozen hex on an enemy unit that deals damage over time, but can be dispelled by moving away from the initial cast point.  If the enemy unit doesn't move outside of the given range, it will be stunned and frozen in place after 4 seconds.

ancient_apparition_ice_vortex.desc: Creates a vortex of icy energy that slows and increases magic damage done to enemies in its range.

ancient_apparition_chilling_touch.desc: Enhances Ancient Apparition's attack with increased range, heavy magic damage, and movement slow.

ancient_apparition_ice_blast.desc: Launches a tracer toward any location on the battlefield, which must be triggered again to mark the area to be blasted by a damaging explosion of hail. The further the tracer travels, the larger the explosion will be. Enemies caught in the explosion, or who touch the icy ball of hail as it travels, are Frostbitten, taking damage and prevented from regenerating or healing. If a Frostbitten unit's health drops below a certain percentage, they will instantly shatter.

ancient_apparition_ice_blast_release.desc: Releases the ice blast to explode at the tracer's current location.

spirit_breaker_charge_of_darkness.desc: Spirit Breaker fixes his sight on an enemy unit and starts charging through all objects.  All enemy units passed through and the targeted unit will be hit by a Greater Bash.  If the targeted unit dies, Spirit Breaker will change his target to the nearest enemy unit to that location.

spirit_breaker_bulldoze.desc: Spirit Breaker gains movement speed and status resistance to ram through enemies. Can be used while charging.

spirit_breaker_empowering_haste.desc: Causes Spirit Breaker to gain power with higher movement speed. His presence increases the movement speed of nearby allied units. Can be cast to improve the movement speed bonus for 6 seconds.

spirit_breaker_greater_bash.desc: Gives a chance to stun and knockback an enemy unit on an attack. Deals a percentage of movement speed as damage.

spirit_breaker_nether_strike.desc: Spirit Breaker slips into the nether realm, reappearing next to his hapless victim. Upon reappearing, a Greater Bash of the current level occurs and deals bonus damage. Knocks back for double the normal distance.

ursa_earthshock.desc: Ursa leaps forward 250 units and slams the earth, causing a powerful shock to damage and slow all enemy units in a nearby area for 4 seconds.

ursa_overpower.desc: Using his skill in combat, Ursa gains increased attack speed for a number of subsequent attacks.

ursa_fury_swipes.desc: Ursa's claws dig deeper wounds in the enemy, causing consecutive attacks to the same enemy to deal more damage.  If the same target is not attacked after 8,12,16,20 seconds, the bonus damage is lost.

ursa_enrage.desc:
Ursa goes into a frenzy, providing damage reduction and status resistance. Removes any existing debuffs.

DISPEL TYPE: Strong Dispel

gyrocopter_rocket_barrage.desc: Launches a salvo of rockets at nearby enemy units in a radius around the Gyrocopter.  Lasts 3 seconds.

gyrocopter_homing_missile.desc: Fires a homing missile to seek the targeted enemy unit. The missile gains speed over time, dealing damage and stunning when it impacts the target. Enemy units can destroy the missile before it reaches its target.

gyrocopter_flak_cannon.desc: Gyrocopter's attacks hit all enemy units in an area around it for a limited number of attacks.  Only the main target of attacks will receive attack bonuses such as Critical Strike.  Lasts 10 seconds or until the attacks are used.

gyrocopter_call_down.desc: Call down an aerial missile strike on enemy units in a target area. After 2 seconds, two missiles arrive in succession, with 2 seconds between them.

alchemist_berserk_potion.desc: Alchemist throws a potion at an ally, applying a basic dispel and giving them 50 Attack Speed and 40 HP regen.Lasts 10 seconds.

alchemist_acid_spray.desc: Sprays high-pressure acid across a target area. Enemy units who step across the contaminated terrain take damage per second and have their armor reduced.

alchemist_unstable_concoction.desc: Alchemist brews up an unstable concoction that he can throw at an enemy hero, to stun and deal damage in an area around the explosion. The longer the concoction brews, the more damage it deals and the longer the stun. After 5 seconds, the brew reaches its maximum damage and stun time. However, after 5.5 seconds, the concoction will explode on Alchemist himself if not thrown.

alchemist_unstable_concoction_throw.desc: Throw it before it blows up!

alchemist_goblins_greed.desc: Alchemist synthesizes additional gold from his enemies and bounty runes. With each kill, Alchemist earns base bonus gold and extra bonus gold. If Alchemist kills another unit which yields gold within the next 36 seconds, an additional instance of Extra Bonus Gold is added to the total. Additionally, causes bounty runes to yield more gold.

alchemist_chemical_rage.desc:
Alchemist causes his Ogre to enter a chemically induced rage, reducing base attack cooldown and increasing movement speed and health regeneration.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

invoker_quas.desc: Allows manipulation of ice elements. Each Quas instance provides increased health regeneration.

invoker_wex.desc: Allows manipulation of storm elements. Each Wex instance provides increased attack speed and movement speed.

invoker_exort.desc: Allows manipulation of fire elements. Each Exort instance provides increased attack damage.

invoker_empty1.desc: Casting Invoke will replace this slot with one of ten unique spells based on Invoker's currently active Quas, Wex, and Exort buffs.

invoker_empty2.desc: Casting Invoke will replace this slot with one of ten unique spells based on Invoker's currently active Quas, Wex, and Exort buffs.

invoker_invoke.desc: Combines the properties of the elements currently being manipulated to create a new spell for Invoker to use. Invoke cooldown is reduced by 0.3 seconds for each orb level.  Click the help button to see the list of possible spells.

invoker_attribute_bonus.desc: Improves all attributes per point spent

invoker_cold_snap.desc: Invoker draws the heat from an enemy, chilling them to their very core for a duration based on the level of Quas. The enemy will take damage and be briefly frozen. Further damage taken in this state will freeze the enemy again, dealing bonus damage. The enemy can only be frozen so often, but the freeze cooldown decreases based on the level of Quas.

invoker_ghost_walk.desc: Invoker manipulates the ice and electrical energies around him, rendering his body invisible. The elemental imbalance created as a consequence slows nearby enemies based on the level of Quas, and slows Invoker as well based on the level of Wex.

invoker_tornado.desc:
Unleashes a fast moving tornado that picks up enemy units in its path, suspending them helplessly in the air shortly before allowing them to plummet to their doom. Travels further based on the level of Wex. Holds enemies in the air for a duration based on the level of Quas. Deals base damage plus added damage based on levels in Wex.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

invoker_emp.desc: Invoker builds up a charge of electromagnetic energy at a targeted location which automatically detonates after 2.9 seconds. The detonation covers an area, draining mana based on the level of Wex. Deals damage for each point of mana drained.  If EMP drains mana from an enemy hero, Invoker gains 50% of the mana drained.

invoker_alacrity.desc: Invoker infuses an ally with an immense surge of energy, increasing their attack speed based on the level of Wex and their damage based on the level of Exort.

invoker_chaos_meteor.desc: Invoker pulls a flaming meteor from space onto the targeted location. Upon landing, the meteor rolls forward, constantly dealing damage based on the level of Exort, and rolling further based on the level of Wex. Units hit by the meteor will also be set on fire for a short time, receiving additional damage based on the level of Exort.

invoker_sun_strike.desc: Sends a catastrophic ray of fierce energy from the sun at any targeted location, incinerating all enemies standing beneath it once it reaches the earth. Deals damage based on the level of Exort, however this damage is spread evenly over all enemies hit.

invoker_forge_spirit.desc: Invoker forges a spirit embodying the strength of fire and fortitude of ice. Damage and armor are based on the level of Exort while attack range, health, and duration are based on the level of Quas. The elemental's scorching attack is capable of melting the armor of enemy heroes. Spawns two spirits when Quas and Exort are at least level 4.

forged_spirit_melting_strike.desc: Melts away the armor of heroes hit by the spirit's attack. Each successive hit increases the amount of armor melted.

invoker_ice_wall.desc: Generates a wall of solid ice directly in front of Invoker for a duration based on the level of Quas. The bitter cold emanating from it greatly slows nearby enemies based on the level of Quas and deals damage each second based on the level of Exort.

invoker_deafening_blast.desc: Invoker unleashes a mighty sonic wave in front of him, dealing damage to any enemy unit it collides with based on the level of Exort. The sheer impact from the blast is enough to knock those enemy units back for a duration based on the level of Quas, then disarm their attacks for a duration based on the level of Wex.

invoker_cold_snap_ad.desc: Invoker draws the heat from an enemy, chilling them to their very core for a duration. The enemy will take damage and be briefly frozen. Further damage taken in this state will freeze the enemy again, dealing bonus damage. The enemy can only be frozen so often, but the freeze cooldown decreases as the level goes up.

invoker_ghost_walk_ad.desc: Invoker manipulates the ice and electrical energies around him, rendering his body invisible. The elemental imbalance created as a consequence slows nearby enemies, and slows Invoker as well based on the level.

invoker_tornado_ad.desc:
Unleashes a fast moving tornado that picks up enemy units in its path, suspending them helplessly in the air shortly before allowing them to plummet to their doom. Travels further based on the level and holds enemies in the air for a duration.

DISPEL TYPE: Basic Dispel

invoker_emp_ad.desc: Invoker builds up a charge of electromagnetic energy at a targeted location which automatically detonates after 2.9 seconds. The detonation covers an area, draining mana. Deals damage for each point of mana drained.  If EMP drains mana from an enemy hero, Invoker gains 50% of the mana drained.

invoker_alacrity_ad.desc: Invoker infuses an ally with an immense surge of energy, increasing their attack speed and their damage.

invoker_sun_strike_ad.desc: Sends a catastrophic ray of fierce energy from the sun at any targeted location, incinerating all enemies standing beneath it once it reaches the earth. Damage is spread evenly over all enemies hit.

invoker_forge_spirit_ad.desc: Invoker forges a spirit embodying the strength of fire and fortitude of ice. The elemental's scorching attack is capable of melting the armor of enemy heroes.

invoker_chaos_meteor_ad.desc: Invoker pulls a flaming meteor from space onto the targeted location. Upon landing, the meteor rolls forward, constantly dealing damage and rolling further based on the level. Units hit by the meteor will also be set on fire for a short time.

invoker_ice_wall_ad.desc: Generates a wall of solid ice directly in front of Invoker for a duration. The bitter cold emanating from it greatly slows nearby enemies and deals damage each second.

invoker_deafening_blast_ad.desc: Invoker unleashes a mighty sonic wave in front of him, dealing damage to any enemy unit it collides with. The sheer impact from the blast is enough to knock those enemy units back for a duration then disarm their attacks for a duration.

silencer_curse_of_the_silent.desc: Curses the target area, causing enemy heroes to take damage and slowing their movement speed. Anytime affected enemies cast a spell, the duration is increased.

silencer_glaives_of_wisdom.desc: Silencer enchants his glaives with his wisdom, dealing additional damage based on his Intelligence. Silencer temporarily steals his target's Intelligence with each hit.

silencer_last_word.desc: Enchants a target, providing vision of them and causing them to be damaged and silenced if they cast a spell or if the enchantment timer expires. Deals extra damage based on the difference in intelligence between Silencer and the target.

silencer_global_silence.desc: Silencer stops all sound, preventing enemy heroes and units on the map from casting spells.

obsidian_destroyer_arcane_orb.desc: Adds extra pure damage to Outworld Destroyer's attacks, based on his remaining mana pool.

obsidian_destroyer_astral_imprisonment.desc: Places a target unit into an astral prison. The hidden unit is invulnerable and disabled. When the astral prison implodes, it deals damage to the target and steals a percentage of their max mana.

obsidian_destroyer_essence_aura.desc: Whenever nearby allied Heroes or Outworld Destroyer itself casts a spell, it gains a chance to restore a percentage of its mana pool.  Outworld Destroyer also passively gains a bonus to its base mana pool.  Several skills with no cooldown and toggled spells cannot trigger Essence Aura.

obsidian_destroyer_equilibrium.desc: Passively grants you a chance to restore a percentage of your max mana each time you cast an ability.

obsidian_destroyer_sanity_eclipse.desc: Unleashes a psychic blast that deals to enemies based on the difference between your mana and the target's mana. Sanity's Eclipse can hit units trapped by Astral Imprisonment.

lycan_summon_wolves.desc: Summons two wolves to fight for Lycan.  Level 3-4 wolves have Permanent Invisibility, and level 4 wolves have Cripple.

lycan_wolf_bite.desc: Lycan bites an ally, granting them Shapeshift properties. Lycan and the bitten target gain 30% Lifesteal and share 30% Lifesteal with each other as long as they are within 1200 range of each other.

lycan_howl.desc: Strikes fear into enemies, reducing armor and attack damage to all enemies within 2000 range of Lycan and his wolves.

lycan_feral_impulse.desc: Increases the HP regeneration and damage of Lycan and all units under his control.

lycan_shapeshift.desc: Lycan assumes his lupine form, granting him and his units critical strikes and added vision at night. During Shapeshift, Lycan and all units under his control move at increased speed, cannot be slowed and have a 40% chance to deal a critical strike doing 150,175,200% damage.

lycan_summon_wolves_critical_strike.desc: Gives 20% to cripple the target, causing 8 damage per second and lose 60 Attack Speed for 4 seconds.

lone_druid_spirit_bear.desc:
Summons a powerful Spirit Bear companion that can equip items.  If the bear moves 1100 distance away from the Lone Druid, it cannot attack.  Lone Druid suffers 20% of his max health as backlash damage if the Spirit Bear dies. Spirit Bear does not benefit from attributes.
Spirit Bear has the Return, Demolish and Entangling Roots abilities.

lone_druid_rabid.desc: Increases the attack and movement speed of Lone Druid and the Spirit Bear.

lone_druid_spirit_link.desc: Links Lone Druid and the Spirit Bear, increasing the attack speed of both and causing damage dealt by the Spirit Bear to heal Lone Druid.

lone_druid_savage_roar.desc: Lone Druid and the Spirit Bear roar fiercely causing nearby enemies to flee towards their base in terror. Their movement speed is increased by 20%.

lone_druid_savage_roar_bear.desc: Lone Druid and the Spirit Bear roar fiercely causing nearby enemies to flee towards their base in terror. Their movement speed is increased by 20%.

lone_druid_true_form.desc: Lone Druid learns to morph himself into a raging bear, losing his ranged advantage, but gaining increased resistance, Entangling Roots and Demolish.

lone_druid_true_form_battle_cry.desc: Adds attack damage and armor to the Lone Druid as well as any nearby units under his control.

lone_druid_spirit_bear_return.desc: Channels for 3 seconds and then teleports the Spirit Bear back to the Lone Druid.

lone_druid_spirit_bear_entangle.desc: Attacks have a chance to cause roots to burst from the ground, immobilizing the attacked enemy unit, and dealing damage per second.

lone_druid_entangling_claws.desc: Cause roots to burst from the ground, immobilizing the target enemy unit and causes them to take more damage from attacks. Enemies can still move and attack while entangled.

lone_druid_spirit_bear_defender.desc: Spirit Bear absorbs 30% of the damage dealt to Lone Druid.

lone_druid_spirit_bear_demolish.desc: Increases the power of the Spirit Bear, causing it to deal more damage to buildings and have additional spell resistance.

brewmaster_thunder_clap.desc: Slams the ground, dealing damage and slowing the movement speed and attack rate of nearby enemy units.

brewmaster_drunken_haze.desc: Drenches a target in alcohol, causing their movement speed to be reduced, and causing their attacks to have a chance to miss.

brewmaster_cinder_brew.desc: Drenches an area in alcohol, causing enemy units to move slower and ignited once they take any spell damage. Duration is increased by 3 seconds when ignited.

brewmaster_drunken_brawler.desc: Brewmaster passively gains a chance to evade physical attacks and deal critical damage when attacking.  When activated, Brewmaster goes into a drunken brawler state, granting him increased chance to evade or deal critical damage.
